Contact us

Want to get in touch? We’d love to help you live simply healthy. Here’s how you can reach us

Healthylife

Customer Care

Contact our friendly Customer Care team by clicking the 'Need help?' tab, and chat to a team member within minutes, between 8:30am and 5:00pm AEST, Monday to Friday.

Alternatively, email us at care@healthylife.com.au for a response within 4 hours, or call 1300 463 342 to speak to an agent between 8:30am to 5:00pm AEST, Monday to Friday.

Media and PR

media@healthylife.com.au

Suppliers

buying@healthylife.com.au

Privacy and Personal Information

privacy@woolworths.com.au

FAQs and Healthylife Help Centre

Got a question? Check out our FAQs page or head to the Healthylife Help Centre.

If you can’t find the answer you need contact our Customer support team by clicking on the ‘chat with us’ button.

Healthylife Pharmacy

If you have an enquiry regarding an order for Pharmacy Only items (including prescriptions), or any pharmacy-related questions, contact the friendly Healthylife Pharmacy Customer Care team by emailing care@healthylifepharmacy.com.au, or calling 1300 463 342 and press 2 for the pharmacy team.

Healthylife Pharmacy Customer Care operating hours are 8.30am to 4.30pm AEST, Monday to Friday.
